#CakePHP Component for blocking malicious IP addresses
Updated by Randy Bonds Jr to CakePHP 2.x

##Instructions
Enter your [http:BL api key](http://www.projecthoneypot.org/httpbl_configure.php) here:  
app/config/bootstrap.php

Place your honeypot php file here:  
app/webroot/

Use ``$this->blockMalicious()`` in your controller (best in AppController::beforeFilter)

Use 
`` <?php echo $this->HttpBlacklist->honeyPot(); ?>``